{"type":"message","id":"ff4d1b93","parentId":"94fd9171","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:41:09.180Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来使用aria引用在点击时可能会失效。让我尝试使用JavaScript来获取页面的URL结构和文档链接，然后直接访问这些链接，而不是通过点击导航。\n\n我可以尝试使用web_fetch工具直接访问文档页面，但首先需要知道文档的URL模式。让我检查当前页面的URL结构。\n\n或者，我可以使用浏览器的evaluate功能来提取所有文档链接的href属性。让我试试这个方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我使用JavaScript来提取所有文档链接："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_96e4ef68f6ad4a948de93d90","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"evaluate","targetId":"153D9CA72E812CAF2DD464B72F05E7C8","fn":"\n// 提取所有文档链接\nconst links = [];\nconst allLinks = document.querySelectorAll('a[href*=\"/knowledge/\"]');\nallLinks.forEach(link => {\n  const text = link.textContent.trim();\n  const href = link.href;\n  if (text && href && !links.some(l => l.href === href)) {\n    links.push({text, href});\n  }\n});\nreturn JSON.stringify(links.slice(0, 50)); // 先获取前50个\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":167,"output":237,"cacheRead":45184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45588,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774082456529}}
